With all due respect to the artists and the creators.
If you can't have variety of music representing all the cultures in Pakistan, you better rename the Coke Studio to "Punjabi Studio". 
Since last few seasons, almost 80% songs are in punjabi, even artists of non-punjabi ethnicity are forced to sing punjabi songs. 
Nothing against punjabees or their music. Lekin diversity bhi koi cheez hoti hay!
